                          <li class="list-item-1">Walk/bike/bus for __% of travels per (week/month)</li>
                          <li class="list-item-1">Purchase an Electronic Vehicle</li>
                          <li class="list-item-1">Install an Electronic Vehicle charging station in your yard</li>
                      </ul>
                  </div>
                  <br>
                  <br>

                   <button class="collapsible"><h4 class="heading-color-adjustment">Renewable Energy</h4></button>
