                         <li class="list-item-1">Schedule an energy retrofit consultation for my house</li>
                         <li class="list-item-1">Add solar panels on south-facing roofs of my home</li>
                         <li class="list-item-1">Install __ energy retrofits in my place in the next __</li>
                     </ul>
                  </div>
                  <br>
                  <br>

